r acting as President , during the term within which this article becomes operative from holding the office of President or acting as President during the remainder of such term . This article shall be inoperative unless it shall have been ratified as an amendment to the Constitution by the legislatures of three - fourths of the several states within seven years from the date of its submission to the states by the Congress .	0
