ction thereof for beverage purposes is hereby prohibited . The Congress and the several states shall have concurrent power to enforce this article by appropriate legislation . This article shall be inoperative unless it shall have been ratified as an amendment to the Constitution by the legislatures of the several states , as provided in the Constitution , within seven years from the date of the submission hereof to the states by the Congress .	0
